<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="floor" id="floor">floor</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
语法：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">floor</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> arg <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

函数 floor() 返回不大于arg的最大整数。例如，
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">     y <span class="sy1">=</span> <span class="nu16">6.04</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
     x <span class="sy1">=</span> <span class="kw3">floor</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> y <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

将会导致x被设置为 6.0, 并且

</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">     y <span class="sy1">=</span> <span class="sy2">-</span><span class="nu16">6.04</span><span class="sy4">;</span>
     x <span class="sy1">=</span> <span class="kw3">floor</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> y <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

将会设置x为 -7.0.
</p>

<p>
C++ 也提供了下列重载形式：

</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cmath&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">float</span> <span class="kw3">floor</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">float</span> arg <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span> <span class="co1">// same as floorf() in C99</span>
    <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> <span class="kw3">floor</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">long</span> <span class="kw4">double</span> arg <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span> <span class="co1">// same as floorl() in C99</span></pre>
<p>
相关主题： <a href="ceil" class="wikilink1" title="cn:numeric:c:ceil">ceil</a>, <a href="fmod" class="wikilink1" title="cn:numeric:c:fmod">fmod</a>
</p>

